    "description": "Create a professional website for a psychologist named “Dr. Elena Rivera”.\n\nService:\nShe offers individual therapy for adults dealing with anxiety, stress, and life transitions.\n\nAudience:\nAdults looking for emotional support and a safe space to talk.\n\nTone:\nWarm, calm, empathetic, human. Not corporate or salesy.\n\nMain colors:\n- Soft sage green (primary)\n- Beige or warm cream backgrounds\n- Soft gray text\n- Light muted teal accents\n\nGoals:\nEncourage visitors to book a first consultation.\n\nStructure:\n- Hero with gentle, reassuring headline\n- About section introducing Dr. Elena\n- Services section (anxiety, stress, personal growth)\n- “How therapy works” section\n- Testimonials (written respectfully and realistically)\n- Contact / booking CTA\n- FAQ section\n\nDesign guidance:\n- Calm, spacious layout\n- Use lots of whitespace\n- Natural imagery (plants, soft light, calm environments)\n- Avoid flashy animations\n\nCopy guidance:\n- Compassionate language\n- Focus on safety and trust\n- Avoid clinical or cold wording\n- No hype or exaggerated claims\n\nMake it feel like a safe, welcoming space.\nMake the layout realistic and professional.",
